Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,久違的陸地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳踏實地的感覺真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然熱血的我還是最適合這廣袤的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的熱血也只能持續到下個港口為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否改走陸路前往雷之國呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計沒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在身處水之國的境內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由大大小小的島嶼組成的水之國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同雷之國並未接壤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…一想到要乘船就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那離雷之國還有多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概還有四分之一的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 在港口聽聞附近有山寨出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:00:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無怨無仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此相遇就是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下買路財吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個護額是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是來自木葉以身弒曉的漩渦鳴人大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 山寨就是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡像了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們無視我 還在吐槽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是木葉的漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我算個啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連自己是誰都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥你們也帶著木葉的護額呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是真正的漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨真價實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過沒想到竟然山寨鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來名氣十足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能擺平他的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此一決勝負 看看誰才是真正的鳴人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 努力戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了的話他就是真貨咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴倒是囂張得很
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這連熱身運動都算不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西我們沒收了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼處置這個男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在趕路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傢伙 暴打一頓扔路邊就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他逃掉再製造麻煩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可就聲名狼藉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責追蹤這名盜賊 名叫伊己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢和這傢伙對峙的屈指可數
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也就我倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙可是讓人聞風喪膽的大盜賊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙才不是漩渦鳴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了…我才是正品漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你是真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 我的大名竟然被盜賊所用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太混蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你在追蹤這盜賊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是官府人士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後就拜託這位大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕緊上路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大哥…你沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來可沒有那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可貌相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是忍者大師伊已大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來您這麼牛逼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不能以貌取人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是被幹掉了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想幹掉他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是真正的漩渦鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到會在這裡遇到真貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邦納 你的借口我不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來計劃好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幹掉身為盜賊的你 從而提升我的名望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在即將打響的戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有名望可無法展現自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果幹掉漩渦鳴人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能大名遠揚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…這麼危險的事打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你的恩惠你都忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在一個人孤獨地哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊己是我唯一的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過下次要找我們能幹掉的做對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫我們能幹掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我動真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它是一個還是兩個漩渦鳴人 都不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我吧 伊己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了就好 能明白的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人在這附近當山賊是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有數人遇險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是個大紅臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為何鳴人會在這裡做山賊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是拯救了村子的英雄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有傳言說漩渦鳴人在村裡是個麻煩的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許成為叛忍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果叛離村子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉應當也在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他再轉賣給木葉 一定能有個好價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒問題嗎 對方可是漩渦鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說漩渦鳴人連中忍考試都沒通過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕那英雄傳說也是捏造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於身為傭兵忍者的我們而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是財源吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我拿出真本領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒必要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一來 看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了社會 為了人民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保衛世界和平的偉大忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊己大爺就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊己真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊己如果動真格的 一定很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能在戰場上鶴立雞群
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要做農活 我要當英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來你又是漩渦鳴人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 邦納…不是 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有獵物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行商人你該不會輸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無怨無仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此相遇就是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我漩渦鳴人留下買路財吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實放下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那些傢伙不是旅行商人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會自動送上門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙才不是漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是個廢物盜賊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這傢伙的外貌符合消息所述
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還帶有木葉的護額
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這傢伙的同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢來搗亂的話 連你一起收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒那回…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…我是漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙才不是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深山老林裡出來的農二代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願幹農活 以為自己是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天想抓我出名 死纏不休
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邦納
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山寨忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然連你一起收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子終於不鬧騰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕緊趕路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們交給我的盜賊被其他的盜賊給劫走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想請你們替我奪回那個盜賊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是忍者大師來著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己動手不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…現在…我有點…不在狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者還要看什麼狀態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我們有急事必須走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且你是官府中人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回衙門找人幫忙不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是盜賊搶走盜賊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也就是窩裡反而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙雖然是個壞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也並非窮凶極惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙因為外表凶悍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被大家討厭 欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去就一直很膽小 很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善於照顧他人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當瞭解那傢伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是官府中人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就讓人覺得很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我老實坦白所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所有的經過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥做這種蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 幫幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拯救了木葉的英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他是同伴 為什麼讓他做這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他是同伴 為什麼不替他想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不是什麼同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是圖個方便才不會理他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是什麼同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你而言 那傢伙算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你一直把他當笨蛋耍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那傢伙從小就和你在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同走到現在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不算同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有時間確實可以聽聽你的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們不能輕易暴露身份和所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你忘記見到過我們的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 拜託了 我一個人辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莫能助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…是同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊己 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是這傢伙的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是同伴 也不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是我的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邦納 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不救你的話 我們的計劃可就擱淺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那樣的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像個鬼一樣被大家厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有伊己願意和我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 我也被其他人欺負啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說只要我整你 就不會再欺負我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊己跟我成為了摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來 漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們看看我們最後的志氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡 我都會跟著伊己的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼點本事還想贏我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活捉漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個不用留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能像漩渦鳴人那樣厲害就能保護伊己了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邦納…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邦納
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你把我當成你的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邦納
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們兩個 看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時僅憑你的隻言片語無法讓人信服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就試探了你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試探我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在非常感動 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有棄朋友於不顧 信任朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位大爺 你們以為是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位傳說中的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是保護了木葉的英雄 漩渦鳴人大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給力點 你可是鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是天下的英雄 漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人 一生一次的大暴動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把漩渦鳴人的名字還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名號我可傷不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們接下來想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會經歷如此恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不太適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要回故鄉去過平凡的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能和伊己一起 去哪兒都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂地活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摯友真好啊
